Blocks.Text: Each interaction pattern represents an AND relationship between variables, thus
can be taken as a symbolic concept encoded by the DNN.
The "torso" exists if and only if all pixels in S1 are present,
then the model obtain the marginal utility I (S1)
Note that this study also extracts the OR interaction, which is proved to be a specific AND interaction.
